前做足準備，除出動保安和警員戒備，更以防範流感為由，要求握手的粉絲當場噴消毒藥水，再被現場保安檢查雙手，以免出現精液手和優子接觸。另外，去年成員渡邊麻友來港出席壽司活動時，有粉絲懶理規矩與麻友合照和抱抱，期間有男狂迷下跪示愛，該狂迷除被保安趕離現場，更遭在樓上看熱鬧的粉絲淋水，幸麻友未受影響。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你諗下呢件事發生係15歲o靚妹身上有幾嘔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6879879942fb5ca6578c3b6c9a68733a8892bc51","tid":451892,"uid":581,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T21:03:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/30/001038_11ce914a88d22832114e079456a08882.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F30%2F001038_11ce914a88d22832114e079456a08882.jpg&h=cac31620&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd5e3593ba5ab2d291c28cd288bcdd21060e4a6a","tid":451892,"uid":15497,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T23:30:18.000Z","msg":"裴珠泫最正"},{"pid":"32633e8b103dca915372e50f70821a14787070bb","tid":451892,"uid":11890,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T23:57:23.000Z","msg":"班毒撚真係好撚恐怖呀<br />\n同個女仔三唔識七就叫人做雞下海拍av<br />\n<br />\n你諗下呢件事發生係15歲o靚妹身上有幾嘔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aac05d81bf0fdf344605657e41634606b7566f63","tid":451892,"uid":33004,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T00:01:47.000Z","msg":"akb毒撚同韓狗一樣恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81d6390deb04e705d95786e3a83b255cb1